1 (1) A law enforcement official from performing the law
2 enforcement official's duties under state law,
3 including investigating or enforcing state criminal
4 laws;
5 (2) Compliance with a judicial warrant, court order, or
6 subpoena; or
7 (3) The provision of information or assistance expressly
8 required by federal or state law, including any
9 mandatory information-sharing duty, or in accordance
10 with title 8 United States Code sections 1373 and
11 1644."
12 SECTION 3. This Act does not affect rights and duties that
13 matured, penalties that were incurred, and proceedings that were
14 begun before its effective date.
15 SECTION 4. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
